title: AUD/USD Outlook Positive As We Reach 6775/80
text:
AUD/USD And NZD/USD Spot Daily Forecast - October 7, 2019

AUDUSD & NZDUSD Spot Chart

outlook positive as we reach 6775/80 and a selling opportunity at 6800/10, with stops above 6825. Be ready to buy a break above 6825 targeting 6845/50 and 6870/75.

First support at 6745/40 then a buying opportunity at 6725/20; stops below 6705.

selling opportunity at 6340/50, with stops above 6370. Be ready to buy a break above 6370 for a buy signal targeting 6400/05 and 6440/50.

Buy at 6280/70, with stops below 6255.
